item.title: By: Ronnie
item.dc:creator: Ronnie
item.description: Hey, I followed your signature on Zilvia to here, and I must say, I'm very impressed with your thoroughness with your vehicles, and the attention to detail. I absolutely love your FD, and I'm sure the S13 will not fail to impress. I have some of the Voodoo arms on my car as well, and I love them. Can't wait to see what you do with the S13, man. Keep up the awesome work, and the great narrative.
item.content:encoded: Hey, I followed your signature on Zilvia to here, and I must say, I’m very impressed with your thoroughness with your vehicles, and the attention to detail. I absolutely love your FD, and I’m sure the S13 will not fail to impress. I have some of the Voodoo arms on my car as well, and I love them. Can’t wait to see what you do with the S13, man. Keep up the awesome work, and the great narrative.
